msgid ""
"This module provides streaming media server support for MP4 files. User "
"can send a HTTP request to the server with ``start`` argument which is "
"measured in seconds, and the server will respond with the stream such "
"that its start position corresponds to the requested time, for example::"
msgstr ""

# 87f27616e4bf401d84706428004531e3
#: ../../admin-guide/plugins/mp4.en.rst:31
msgid ""
"This allows performing a random seeking at any time. We can use flash "
"player, vlc, mplayer, firefox or chrome to play the streaming media."
msgstr ""

